	   arj_proc.h, arj_user.c, ea_mgr.c, encode.c, environ.c,
	   environ.h, filelist.c, filelist.h, makefile, misc.c, misc.h,
	   msgbind.c, rearj.c, recovery.c, scrnio.h: Merged with MetaWare
	   High C branch.

